{"type":"message","id":"632d8669","parentId":"1b80b070","timestamp":"2026-06-04T03:52:10.323Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All submodules are updated. Now I need to spawn a sub-agent to run the Unity hot update pipeline. The sub-agent must use a bat file, not inline PowerShell.\n\nLet me spawn the sub-agent with the task to run the hot update pipeline.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"所有子模块已更新完毕。现在启动子 session 跑 Unity 热更流水线。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_0TCc3cnBwMEb1hCeG25M5549","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"执行 Unity 热更流水线更新测试服\n\n请在 C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace 目录下执行以下步骤：\n\n1. 在 E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv 目录下运行 RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat\n   （直接用 exec 执行 \"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat\"，不需要包裹 cmd /c 或 powershell）\n\n2. 等待 Unity 构建完成（注意 yieldMs 设大一些，比如 600000ms/10 分钟）\n\n3. 构建完成后，扫描日志文件检查错误：\n   ```\n   powershell -Command \"Select-String -Path 'E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log' -Pattern 'error CS\\d+:|git更新失败|Build completed with'\"\n   ```\n\n4. 结果处理：\n   - ✅ **成功**（无错误匹配 + Unity 退出码 0）→ 发送群消息通知\n     命令：`node scripts/feishu_send_group.mjs oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77 hotupdate-ok`\n   - ❌ **失败**（有错误匹配或 Unity 退出码非 0）→ 用 sessions_send 私聊通知主人结果，**不在群里发失败消息**\n\n5. 通知完成后，用 sessions_send 回传结果给我（sessionKey 我会在创建后提供）。\n\n重要提示：\n- Unity 路径会自动读取 bat 中的配置\n- 这是增量构建模式，不清 Bundles 缓存\n- 注意检查 bat 文件的执行输出，等待 Unity 进程完成","mode":"run","label":"hotupdate"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":209,"output":530,"cacheRead":25472,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26211,"cost":{"input":0.00002926,"output":0.0001484,"cacheRead":0.000713216,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0008908760000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780545126070,"responseId":"72fc69cf-04ef-4f03-9346-66b9832fc59d"}}
