{"type":"message","id":"02f70b83","parentId":"e76acde7","timestamp":"2026-06-04T09:06:46.197Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人让我检查 TAPD 和 GitLab 的 cookie 活性。我需要运行对应的保活/检查脚本看看 cookie 是否有效。\n\n对于 TAPD：\n- 周以天账号 cookie: `workspace/tapd_cookies_zhouyitian.json`\n- 叶枝君账号 cookie: `workspace/tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json`\n- 默认主文件: `workspace/tapd_cookies.json`\n\n对于 GitLab：\n- cookie: `workspace/gitlab_cookies.json`\n\n其实保活脚本本身就会检查 cookie 是否有效，但我可以直接用一个轻量的脚本来检查。或者直接跑保活脚本，如果返回码 0 就是有效的。\n\n不过保活脚本会重新请求页面续期，不仅仅检查。我也可以直接用 web_fetch 或者 Playwright 模拟一个请求来检查 cookie 的有效性。\n\n更简单的方式：直接跑保活脚本。如果 cookie 有效，它会成功续期并返回 0。如果无效，返回 1 需要重新登录。\n\n让我同时跑这两个检查。\n\n对于 TAPD，有两个账号要检查：周以天（默认）和叶枝君。\n\n对于 GitLab，有一个账号要检查。\n\n这些都是快速操作，可以在主 session 直接完成。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，同时检查 TAPD（两个账号）和 GitLab 的 cookie 活性~"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_2hK47Vtctr7rBLvMi7TN7514","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace; node scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs 2>&1","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_Uy5cjj6RhBYpwyjqoVFT7198","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace; node scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs yezhijun 2>&1","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_02_fGIbY4YLPLIgPszLtBpc4746","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace; node scripts/gitlab_keepalive.mjs 2>&1","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":7221,"output":536,"cacheRead":21120,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28877,"cost":{"input":0.00101094,"output":0.00015008,"cacheRead":0.00059136,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00175238}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780564000961,"responseId":"31a8dabc-fefb-46d6-a448-934147317fc1"}}
