{"type":"message","id":"060d1317","parentId":"c7a619de","timestamp":"2026-06-04T09:07:13.147Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Results:\n1. **TAPD 周以天** ✅ - 成功续期，tapdsession 有效期到 2026-06-11，退出码 0\n2. **TAPD 叶枝君** ❌ - Cookie 过期，需要重新微信扫码登录，退出码 1\n3. **GitLab** ✅ - 成功续期，Cookie + CSRF Token 都有效，退出码 0\n\n叶枝君的 TAPD cookie 过期了，需要主人重新扫码登录。按照保活方案的描述，失效救援是：用 `headless: false` 跑 Playwright，访问 TAPD 登录页，让主人扫码。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"检查完毕，结果如下：\n\n| 服务 | 账号 | 状态 |\n|------|------|:----:|\n| ✅ **TAPD** | 周以天（提单） | **活性正常**，已续期至 6/11 |\n| ❌ **TAPD** | 叶枝君（需求单） | **Cookie 过期** ❗ |\n| ✅ **GitLab** | 叶枝君 | **活性正常**，CSRF 也刷新了 |\n\n---\n\n叶枝君的 TAPD cookie 过期了，这个账号是用来提需求单的。需要我帮你重新扫码登录一下吗？我开 headed 浏览器打开 TAPD 登录页，你扫个码就续上了~"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":552,"output":302,"cacheRead":29184,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30038,"cost":{"input":0.00007728,"output":0.00008456,"cacheRead":0.000817152,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0009789920000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780564030168,"responseId":"6b13724e-6d3f-4ce7-a7e7-054b03c864f9"}}
